== Lattice

Set of all integer linear combination of linearly independent basis vectors.

Lattice can be generated by different basis (good basis: short orthogonal vectors).

=== Idea

Use bad basis as public key and good basis as private key.

=== Problem

Find a non-zero vector with minimal norm according to a basis...

