= Quantum cryptography

Classic computer: bits (0-1)

Quantum computer: Qubit

== Properties

- superposition
  - infinite number of states
  - measurement: qubit collapses
- entanglement (qubit can be link to other) (2^n basis states !)

== Challenges

- collapsing
- qubits are very sensitive to environment

